{"id":101,"count":2,"description":"Explore the timeless charm of Tamil Nadu, a land where spirituality, culture, and heritage come alive. From the towering Dravidian temples of Madurai, Thanjavur, and Kanchipuram, adorned with intricate carvings and gopurams, to the serene beaches of Chennai and Mahabalipuram, Tamil Nadu is a journey into India\u2019s soul. Wander through the French colonial streets of Pondicherry, relax amidst the lush Nilgiri Hills in Ooty and Kodaikanal, and marvel at the UNESCO-listed monuments of Mahabalipuram. Witness the living traditions of Bharatanatyam, Carnatic music, and vibrant festivals that celebrate the state\u2019s rich culture. With its perfect mix of ancient temples, hill stations, beaches, and heritage towns, Tamil Nadu offers an exotic experience that blends spirituality, history, and natural beauty like no other.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/exotic-tamilnadu\/","name":"EXOTIC TAMILNADU","slug":"exotic-tamilnadu","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/EXOTIC-TAMILNADU.png","filesize":769927,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":84308,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":37602,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":186882,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"EXOTIC-TAMILNADU-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":55679,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtri